citations:
    citation-affc-cersei-iii:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Cersei III"
            text_from_source: "A thousand ships! The little queen's brown hair was tousled and uncombed, and the torchlight made her cheeks look flushed."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Midnight war council: Euron Greyjoy's ironborn have seized all four Shield Islands (Greyshield given to Ser Harras Harlaw, Southshield to Andrik the Unsmiling, Greenshield to Maron Volmark, Oakenshield to Nute the Barber). Margaery Tyrell demands the Redwyne fleet be recalled from the Dragonstone siege. Cersei refuses. Ser Loras Tyrell then volunteers to take Dragonstone by storm, which Cersei permits — knowing the assault will likely kill or gravely wound him, removing a political rival."
